Migration is for creating db tables and columns, for editing/updating/adding db tables and columns.
To make database setup consistent with team mates.
Has instructions for database setup.

php artisan migrate
sqlite3 storage/database.sqlite
	sqlite> .tables
	sqlite> .schema

php artisan //shows commands

php artisan migrate:rollback  // undo

php artisan help make:migration
php artisan make:migration create_articles_table --create="articles"
php artisan make:migration add_excerpt_to_articles_table --table="articles"   //add new column to table articles
